   <taskbody>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <note class="- topic/note ">The LED test is available for all user access levels,
it does not require a login.</note>
      </context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Press the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Double arrow icon</uicontrol> to expand
the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Virtual LED bar</uicontrol>.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Press the <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">LED test</uicontrol> button at the bottom of the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Virtual LED bar</uicontrol> to start the test.</cmd>
         </step>
      </steps>
      <result class="- topic/section task/result ">The test will illuminate all the virtual LEDs and flash the
physical LED above the display for a few seconds. Check that all virtual
LEDs are illuminated in their correct color and that the physical
LED above the display flashes in all four colors (green, yellow, red
and blue).</result>
